description: Tryptic digestion proteomics gives limited coverage of many protein sequences as many proteins produce tryptic peptides that cannot be observed easily. Confetti is our comprehensive map of coverage for the HeLa proteome, using 48 different digests and CID/HCD LC-MS/MS analyses.

terms.name: Reference
terms.value: Guo X, Trudgian DC, Lemoff A, Yadavalli S, Mirzaei H. Confetti: a multiprotease map of the HeLa proteome for comprehensive proteomics. Mol Cell Proteomics. 2014 Jun;13(6):1573-84

title: Confetti: A Multi-protease Map of the HeLa Proteome for Comprehensive Proteomics
